# requirements
1.server -t2.micro
2.install maven and java
3.install docker

# steps1:
step1:
launch a server t2.micro and update
install java and maven tools into server
(apt install openjdk-17-jre-headless  # version 17.0.10~6ea-1) & (apt install maven)
clone the repository and go to into repo
execute maven lifecycles without test(-DskipTests=true)
after execution get target folder and in target folder artifacry is there

# step2:
install docker 
(apt install docker.io)
write a docker file with copy instruction (copying of artifactory)
build the docker image and run as container with port 8070
(docker build -t sagar .)  & (docker run -d -p 8070:8070 sagar)



